WorkItem.Description:
Currently it is not possible to set a paragraphStyle for text in table cells. This could be enabled if addText method in cell.php in \PHPWord\Section\Table\ is modified the following:

public function addText($text, $style = null, $styleParagraph = null) {
	$text = utf8_encode($text);
	$text = new PHPWord_Section_Text($text, $style, $styleParagraph);
	$this->_elementCollection[] = $text;
	return $text;
}
